{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":36,"text":"I didn't know when I agreed to do this"},{"time":4605,"text":"whether I was expected to talk or to sing."},{"time":10285,"text":"But when I was told that the topic was language,"},{"time":15333,"text":"I felt that I had to speak about something for a moment."}]},{"cues":[{"time":20104,"text":"I have a problem."},{"time":24453,"text":"It's not the worst thing in the world."},{"time":26467,"text":"I'm fine."},{"time":27664,"text":"I'm not on fire."},{"time":29413,"text":"I know that other people in the world"},{"time":31314,"text":"have far worse things to deal with,"},{"time":35482,"text":"but for me, language and music are"},{"time":41432,"text":"inextricably linked through this one thing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":45867,"text":"And the thing is that I have a stutter."},{"time":53556,"text":"It might seem curious given that I spend"},{"time":56104,"text":"a lot of my life on the stage."},{"time":59902,"text":"One would assume that I'm comfortable"},{"time":62926,"text":"in the public sphere and comfortable here,"},{"time":65358,"text":"speaking to you guys."},{"time":67798,"text":"But the truth is that I've spent\nmy life up until this point"},{"time":72568,"text":"and including this point, living in mortal dread"},{"time":76919,"text":"of public speaking."},{"time":80229,"text":"Public singing, whole different thing. (Laughter)"},{"time":84939,"text":"But we'll get to that in a moment."},{"time":88432,"text":"I've never really talked about it before so explicitly."},{"time":94342,"text":"I think that that's because I've always lived in hope"},{"time":96674,"text":"that when I was a grown-up,"},{"time":99218,"text":"I wouldn't have one."},{"time":105490,"text":"I sort of lived with this idea that when I'm grown,"},{"time":108705,"text":"I'll have learned to speak French,"},{"time":111912,"text":"and when I'm grown, I'll learn\nhow to manage my money,"},{"time":115190,"text":"and when I'm grown, I won't have a stutter,"},{"time":117468,"text":"and then I'll be able to public speak\nand maybe be the prime minister"},{"time":119791,"text":"and anything's possible and, you know."},{"time":123156,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":126556,"text":"So I can talk about it now"},{"time":129605,"text":"because I've reached this point, where —"},{"time":133427,"text":"I mean, I'm 28."},{"time":137367,"text":"I'm pretty sure that I'm grown now."},{"time":139857,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":141679,"text":"And I'm an adult woman"},{"time":143681,"text":"who spends her life as a performer,"},{"time":147757,"text":"with a speech impediment."},{"time":150659,"text":"So, I might as well come clean about it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":154867,"text":"There are some interesting\nangles to having a stutter."},{"time":158849,"text":"For me, the worst thing that can happen"},{"time":162223,"text":"is meeting another stutterer."},{"time":165485,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":168701,"text":"This happened to me in Hamburg, when"},{"time":171908,"text":"this guy, we met and he said,"},{"time":173911,"text":"\"Hello, m-m-m-my name is Joe,\""},{"time":177532,"text":"and I said, \"Oh, hello, m-m-m-my name is Meg.\""},{"time":181793,"text":"Imagine my horror when I realized"},{"time":184450,"text":"he thought I was making fun of him."},{"time":186355,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":192197,"text":"People think I'm drunk all the time."},{"time":197230,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":200630,"text":"People think that I've forgotten their name"},{"time":204306,"text":"when I hesitate before saying it."},{"time":208997,"text":"And it is a very weird thing, because"},{"time":211220,"text":"proper nouns are the worst."},{"time":215459,"text":"If I'm going to use the word\n\"Wednesday\" in a sentence,"},{"time":219249,"text":"and I'm coming up to the word,"},{"time":222152,"text":"and I can feel that I'm going to stutter or something,"},{"time":225121,"text":"I can change the word to \"tomorrow,\""},{"time":228431,"text":"or \"the day after Tuesday,\""},{"time":230490,"text":"or something else."},{"time":232883,"text":"It's clunky, but you can get away with it,"},{"time":237866,"text":"because over time I've developed this"},{"time":240408,"text":"loophole method of using speech"},{"time":244795,"text":"where right at the last minute you"},{"time":247926,"text":"change the thing and you trick your brain."},{"time":252207,"text":"But with people's names, you can't change them."},{"time":255915,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":258593,"text":"When I was singing a lot of jazz,"},{"time":261762,"text":"I worked a lot with a pianist whose name was Steve."},{"time":267285,"text":"As you can probably gather,"},{"time":269899,"text":"S's and T's, together or independently,"},{"time":273173,"text":"are my kryptonite."},{"time":277287,"text":"But I would have to introduce the band"},{"time":279439,"text":"over this rolling vamp,"},{"time":282651,"text":"and when I got around to Steve,"},{"time":285500,"text":"I'd often find myself stuck on the \"St.\""},{"time":291271,"text":"And it was a bit awkward and uncomfortable \nand it totally kills the vibe."},{"time":296959,"text":"So after a few instances of this,"},{"time":299287,"text":"Steve happily became \"Seve,\""},{"time":304387,"text":"and we got through it that way. (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":309887,"text":"I've had a lot of therapy,"},{"time":312238,"text":"and a common form of treatment is to use"},{"time":314525,"text":"this technique that's called smooth speech,"},{"time":319433,"text":"which is where you almost\nsing everything that you say."},{"time":324858,"text":"You kind of join everything together in this"},{"time":327210,"text":"very singsong, kindergarten teacher way,"},{"time":331475,"text":"and it makes you sound very serene,\nlike you've had lots of Valium,"},{"time":335454,"text":"and everything is calm. (Laughter)"},{"time":339246,"text":"That's not actually me."},{"time":342373,"text":"And I do use that. I do."},{"time":345698,"text":"I use it when I have to be on panel shows,"},{"time":352532,"text":"or when I have to do radio interviews,"},{"time":355911,"text":"when the economy of airtime is paramount."},{"time":360774,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":363828,"text":"I get through it that way for my job."},{"time":368216,"text":"But as an artist who feels that their work"},{"time":370933,"text":"is based solely on a platform of honesty"},{"time":376903,"text":"and being real,"},{"time":380937,"text":"that feels often like cheating."}]},{"cues":[{"time":384671,"text":"Which is why before I sing, I wanted to tell you"},{"time":387885,"text":"what singing means to me."},{"time":391544,"text":"It's more than making nice sounds,"},{"time":395595,"text":"and it's more than making nice songs."},{"time":400997,"text":"It's more than feeling known, or understood."},{"time":406531,"text":"It's more than making you feel the things that I feel."},{"time":412696,"text":"It's not about mythology,"},{"time":415385,"text":"or mythologizing myself to you."},{"time":420427,"text":"Somehow, through some miraculous"},{"time":425805,"text":"synaptic function of the human brain,"},{"time":430305,"text":"it's impossible to stutter when you sing."},{"time":435761,"text":"And when I was younger,\nthat was a method of treatment"},{"time":439517,"text":"that worked very well for me,"},{"time":441970,"text":"singing, so I did it a lot."},{"time":447850,"text":"And that's why I'm here today."}]},{"cues":[{"time":451993,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":456358,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":462010,"text":"Singing for me is sweet relief."},{"time":466583,"text":"It is the only time when I feel fluent."},{"time":475430,"text":"It is the only time when what comes out of my mouth"},{"time":478856,"text":"is comprehensively exactly what I intended."},{"time":481448,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":483731,"text":"So I know that this is a TED Talk,"},{"time":486668,"text":"but now i'm going to TED sing."},{"time":490417,"text":"This is a song that I wrote last year."}]},{"cues":[{"time":491976,"text":"Thank you very much. Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":494374,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":507321,"text":"(Piano)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":522819,"text":"♪ I would be a beauty ♪"}]},{"cues":[{"time":526692,"text":"♪ but my nose ♪"}]},{"cues":[{"time":530168,"text":"♪ is slightly too big ♪"}]},{"cues":[{"time":533802,"text":"♪ for my face ♪"}]},{"cues":[{"time":537300,"text":"♪ And I would be a dreamer ♪"}]},{"cues":[{"time":541175,"text":"♪ but my dream ♪"}]},{"cues":[{"time":544640,"text":"♪ is slightly too big ♪"}]},{"cues":[{"time":548251,"text":"♪ for this space ♪"}]},{"cues":[{"time":551840,"text":"♪ And I would be an angel ♪"}]},{"cues":[{"time":555777,"text":"♪ but my halo ♪"}]},{"cues":[{"time":559450,"text":"♪ it pales in the glow ♪"}]},{"cues":[{"time":562886,"text":"♪ of your grace ♪"}]},{"cues":[{"time":566407,"text":"♪ And I would be a joker ♪"}]},{"cues":[{"time":570164,"text":"♪ but that card looks silly when you play ♪"}]},{"cues":[{"time":578939,"text":"♪ your ace ♪"}]},{"cues":[{"time":595701,"text":"♪ I'd like to know ♪"}]},{"cues":[{"time":599469,"text":"♪ Are there stars in hell? ♪"}]},{"cues":[{"time":603238,"text":"♪ And I'd like to know ♪"}]},{"cues":[{"time":606917,"text":"♪ know if you can tell ♪"}]},{"cues":[{"time":610721,"text":"♪ that you make me lose everything I know ♪"}]},{"cues":[{"time":617705,"text":"♪ That I cannot choose to or not let go ♪"}]},{"cues":[{"time":638022,"text":"♪ And I'd stay forever ♪"}]},{"cues":[{"time":642186,"text":"♪ but my home ♪"}]},{"cues":[{"time":645471,"text":"♪ is slightly too far ♪"}]},{"cues":[{"time":649150,"text":"♪ from this place ♪"}]},{"cues":[{"time":651973,"text":"♪ And I swear I tried to ♪"}]},{"cues":[{"time":656327,"text":"♪ slow it down ♪"}]},{"cues":[{"time":659938,"text":"♪ when I am walking at your pace ♪"}]},{"cues":[{"time":666883,"text":"♪ But all I could think ♪"}]},{"cues":[{"time":669168,"text":"♪ idling through the cities ♪"}]},{"cues":[{"time":674616,"text":"♪ do I look pretty in the rain? ♪"}]},{"cues":[{"time":681785,"text":"♪ And I don't know how someone ♪"}]},{"cues":[{"time":685210,"text":"♪ quite so lovely ♪"}]},{"cues":[{"time":688733,"text":"♪ makes me feel ugly ♪"}]},{"cues":[{"time":694391,"text":"♪ So much shame ♪"}]},{"cues":[{"time":703595,"text":"♪ And I'd like to know ♪"}]},{"cues":[{"time":707296,"text":"♪ Are there stars in hell? ♪"}]},{"cues":[{"time":710852,"text":"♪ And I'd like to know ♪"}]},{"cues":[{"time":714624,"text":"♪ know if you can tell ♪"}]},{"cues":[{"time":718282,"text":"♪ that you make me lose everything I know ♪"}]},{"cues":[{"time":725459,"text":"♪ that I cannot choose to or not let go ♪"}]},{"cues":[{"time":760620,"text":"Thank you very much. (Applause)"}]}]}